  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_1",
    "text": "台东盛产一种叫“释迦” 的水果，我在广州也见过，叫 “番荔枝”。对它印象深刻，不 是因为名字古怪，而是因为价 格非一般的贵。这种水果，外 皮突起恰似佛头，故有赖球果、 佛头果、释迦果之称。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1256613739705111,
      0.5177381709347129,
      0.45634920020869824,
      0.6993217033494962
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_3",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.462962956733462,
      0.5177381709347129,
      0.8553791772027773,
      0.7188306779064564
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_2",
    "text": "沿途经过村镇时，不时见",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17636684066036648,
      0.7068251551021731,
      0.45414461470044365,
      0.7278348200096687
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_4",
    "text": "到路边有摆卖释迦的农舍。我在心中琢磨着，到这里了还不品尝一下， 似乎太对不起自己。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13447971600352943,
      0.7338375814118103,
      0.857583762711032,
      0.7818596726289432
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_5",
    "text": "看中一个大户人家，大大的凉棚，路边摆放着一筐筐的释迦，平板 上也摆满了，个个硕大饱满，颇为招惹人啊！",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.136684301511784,
      0.7878624340310847,
      0.857583762711032,
      0.8358845252482175
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_6",
    "text": "一打听，价格果然不菲，新台币要100元一斤。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.18077601167687563,
      0.8418872866503592,
      0.6481481394268468,
      0.8628969515578547
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_7",
    "text": "我让老板娘特意挑选了一粒成熟的释迦给我，75元成交。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17857142616862107,
      0.8704004033105317,
      0.7517636583148121,
      0.8884086875169565
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_8",
    "text": "“这个怎么吃啊？！”我也不怕老板娘笑话我，没吃过就是没吃过，",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.16754849862734814,
      0.8959121392696335,
      0.8553791772027773,
      0.9169218041771291
